snippet: Rafael Nadal, the 2008 Beijing Olympics gold medalist, and former world number one Caroline Wozniacki were among those named in the provisional entry list for the August Rio Games by the International Tennis Federation (ITF) on Thursday....
lead_paragraph: Rafael Nadal, the 2008 Beijing Olympics gold medalist, and former world number one Caroline Wozniacki were among those named in the provisional entry list for the August Rio Games by the International Tennis Federation (ITF) on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Nadal, Wozniacki Included in Olympic Entry List
headline.main: Nadal, Wozniacki Included in Olympic Entry List
